Mutation data of the MSK-MetTropism cohort

Source: R/data.R
data_MSK.Rd

This table contains read counts data and other information from the MSK-MetTropism cohort.

Usage

data(data_MSK)

Format

A data frame with 224890 rows and 21 columns:

Source

MSK-MET at cBioPortal https://www.cbioportal.org/study/summary?id=msk_met_2021
